Package: tmap.sources
Title: Data Sources for 'tmap'
Version: 0.1
LazyData: true
Authors@R: c(
	person("Martijn", "Tennekes", email = "mtennekes@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
	)
Description: 
    Provides support for a variety of spatial data sources in 'tmap', 
    including remote, tiled, and streaming formats. Enables the use 
    of external vector and raster data without requiring full data 
    import, facilitating efficient visualization workflows.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    tmap (>= 4.2),
    sf,
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    freestiler
Remotes:
    walkerke/freestiler
URL: https://github.com/r-tmap/tmap.sources
BugReports: https://github.com/r-tmap/tmap.sources/issues
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
